Don’t admit fault, let the police investigate. ) Move out of the road. ) Don’t agree to anything like repairing the damage, – it could bind you later. How can SCORPION help? Depending on Teboho’s policy, SCORPION will assist by dealing with the insurance company on his behalf.You can strike back legally too!Click here 
